window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>How far would you go to protect your family? As far as Alex Fletcher?</i></b></p> <p><b>In the very near future,</b> an inconceivable attack against the United States will unleash a nightmare across the country - with a vast appetite for chaos and violence.</p> <p><b>Alex Fletcher, former Marine, will wake to this brutally hostile landscape,</b> thrown headfirst into an epic, near-impossible journey to protect and save his family and friends.</p> <p>Join Alex Fletcher, along with his family and friends on this harrowing trip through a world gone mad.</p> <p><b>The Alex Fletcher audiobooks:</b></p> <ul> <li><i>The Jakarta Pandemic</i>, audiobook one</li> <li><i>The Perseid Collapse</i>, audiobook two</li> <li><i>Event Horizon</i>, audiobook three</li> <li><i>Point of Crisis</i>, audiobook four</li> <li><i>Dispatches</i>, audiobook five&nbsp;&nbsp;</li> </ul>"; 
